rep.scrame.controller.command

Interface Command

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddCommand, DisplayHomeScreenCommand, GetCommand, HelpCommand, ListCommand, QuitCommand, UpdateCommand, ViewCommand

    public interface Command
    Interface for command handler. A command stores a group of function calls and functionality that can be invoked when needed by the system to decouple the system's command handling and command invocation.
